Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two traveling adventurers decide to enter a local tournament at a colosseum. The Gauntlet of Trials is a renowned and immensely challenging set of enemies and puzzles. The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gate opens in front of the duo, and a menacing mechanical golem with a crossbow becomes activated.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoran lunges forward attempting to force his blade through the protective plate.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoran’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. He is able to proceed uninjured.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoran’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The path is blocked by a deep puddle of dirty sludge, there is a rope on the other side of the puddle. The adventures would need to not hesitate to make it across to avoid getting stuck.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoyu swims across the puddle to throw the rope across.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoyu was able to make it across the puddle. He passes over the rope.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoyu hesitates too much and manages to get stuck in the sludge. He makes it across but loses some valuables from the belt in the process.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The room begins to fill with toxic gas and there is a keyhole next to the door leading to the next chamber. Writing on the wall suggests the key seems to be in the stomach of a cow corpse next to the door.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoran rummages through the cow carcass to grab the key from the flesh.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoran is able to find the key quickly. He is able to grab the key with ease before the gas takes effect.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoran hesitates but manages to pull the key out of the dead animal's stomach. He suffers damage due to gas inhalation.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gigantic salamander emerges from the shadows, hungry for flesh.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoyu tries to climb on the salamander’s back and wrestle it into a choke hold.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoyu chokes the salamander into unconsciousness. He is unharmed in the encounter.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: The salamander’s giant maw bites Haoyu’s arm. He takes damage, but the salamander cowers into its den.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The floor between the entrance and exit of this chamber is segmented by large tiles with magical symbols. The tiles rest over a sticky tar-like substance.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoyu attempts to rely on his intellect to solve the puzzle of the magical symbols.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoyu correctly identifies the sequence of tiles necessary to get across. He is showered by applause from the crowd.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoyu repeatedly steps on incorrect tiles but manages to make it across. He loses some valuables from his pack to the tar-like substance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>An ogre emerges from a lift in the center of the room
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoran leaps at the ogre, trying to land a killing blow.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoran stabs the ogre in the chest, killing it instantly. He is met by roaring applause from the audience watching from above.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoran stabs the ogre in the chest but fails to kill it instantly. He is bashed by the ogre’s fist dealing damage before it bleeds to death.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>In the following chamber there is an open treasure chest containing gold coins. The chest is also filled with crawling roaches and maggots.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoyu wades through the chest to grab some of the treasure.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoyu is not fazed by the disgusting chest. He finds a considerable amount of gold.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoyu reaches for the chest of coins with bugs. He is grossed out and only manages to grab a small handful of coins.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>Inside the next chamber is puzzle box that requires a sequence of clever moves to open.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoran tries to rely on his intelligence to open the box.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoran was able to successfully open the box finding a valuable gemstone. He adds the gemstone to his pack.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: After too many failed attempts, the box explodes in Haoran’s hand. He suffers damage.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A ditch of dense noxious gas separates the entrance and exit of this chamber. On the entrance wall is a riddle.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoran attempts to use his wit to solve the riddle.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoran announces his answer and a vent expels the gas. He waits for the gas to dissipate before proceeding.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoran announces his answer and nothing happens. He runs across and suffers damage before pulling a lever dissipating the gas.

Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoran tries to clean enough muck off the wall to see the rune.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoran was able to tolerate the smell and cleans off enough for the rune and the walls begin to glow, revealing to him that there are gemstones along the far wall.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoran tries cleaning off the rune but can’t stomach it for long. He takes a small amount of poison damage.

Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoran hesitates but manages to pull the key out of the dead animal's stomach. He suffers damage due to gas inhalation.

Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoran consumes the pile of grub.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoran finishes the grubs with no issues. He grabs the handful of jewels that magically appear in the chalice.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoran eats the grubs, but to his avail, there were no rewards granted.

Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoyu tries to clean off the dagger to their standard and uses it as the offering.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoyu places the dagger on the pedestal. He is rewarded with some gold coins.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: The dagger was not clean enough. When Haoyu placed the dagger on the statue’s pedestal, the statue retaliated by shooting a dart at him causing damage.

Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two traveling adventurers decide to enter a local tournament at a colosseum. The Gauntlet of Trials is a renowned and immensely challenging set of enemies and puzzles. The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gate opens in front of the duo, and a menacing mechanical golem with a crossbow becomes activated.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoran lunges forward attempting to force his blade through the protective plate.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoran’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. He is able to proceed uninjured.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoran’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The path is blocked by a deep puddle of dirty sludge, there is a rope on the other side of the puddle. The adventures would need to not hesitate to make it across to avoid getting stuck.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoyu swims across the puddle to throw the rope across.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoyu was able to make it across the puddle. He passes over the rope.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoyu hesitates too much and manages to get stuck in the sludge. He makes it across but loses some valuables from the belt in the process.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The room begins to fill with toxic gas and there is a keyhole next to the door leading to the next chamber. Writing on the wall suggests the key seems to be in the stomach of a cow corpse next to the door.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoran rummages through the cow carcass to grab the key from the flesh.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoran is able to find the key quickly. He is able to grab the key with ease before the gas takes effect.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoran hesitates but manages to pull the key out of the dead animal's stomach. He suffers damage due to gas inhalation.

Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: The salamander’s giant maw bites Haoyu’s arm. He takes damage, but the salamander cowers into its den.

Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoyu correctly identifies the sequence of tiles necessary to get across. He is showered by applause from the crowd.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoyu repeatedly steps on incorrect tiles but manages to make it across. He loses some valuables from his pack to the tar-like substance.

Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoyu succeeds in solving the puzzle with plenty of time. He escapes without issue.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoyu fails numerous times before succeeding. He must drop some valuables to reach the exit before suffocating.

Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two traveling adventurers decide to enter a local tournament at a colosseum. The Gauntlet of Trials is a renowned and immensely challenging set of enemies and puzzles. The duo will need to rely on their strength and intelligence to make it through unharmed. Each adventurer will be rewarded proportional to performance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gate opens in front of the duo, and a menacing mechanical golem with a crossbow becomes activated.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoran lunges forward attempting to force his blade through the protective plate.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoran’s sword pierces the plate and destroys the construct before it is able to shoot. He is able to proceed uninjured.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoran’s sword grazes the exterior plate. He is shot by the crossbow and is dealt damage.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The path is blocked by a deep puddle of dirty sludge, there is a rope on the other side of the puddle. The adventures would need to not hesitate to make it across to avoid getting stuck.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoyu swims across the puddle to throw the rope across.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoyu was able to make it across the puddle. He passes over the rope.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoyu hesitates too much and manages to get stuck in the sludge. He makes it across but loses some valuables from the belt in the process.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The room begins to fill with toxic gas and there is a keyhole next to the door leading to the next chamber. Writing on the wall suggests the key seems to be in the stomach of a cow corpse next to the door.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoran rummages through the cow carcass to grab the key from the flesh.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoran is able to find the key quickly. He is able to grab the key with ease before the gas takes effect.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoran hesitates but manages to pull the key out of the dead animal's stomach. He suffers damage due to gas inhalation.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A gigantic salamander emerges from the shadows, hungry for flesh.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoyu tries to climb on the salamander’s back and wrestle it into a choke hold.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoyu chokes the salamander into unconsciousness. He is unharmed in the encounter.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: The salamander’s giant maw bites Haoyu’s arm. He takes damage, but the salamander cowers into its den.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The floor between the entrance and exit of this chamber is segmented by large tiles with magical symbols. The tiles rest over a sticky tar-like substance.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoyu attempts to rely on his intellect to solve the puzzle of the magical symbols.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoyu correctly identifies the sequence of tiles necessary to get across. He is showered by applause from the crowd.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoyu repeatedly steps on incorrect tiles but manages to make it across. He loses some valuables from his pack to the tar-like substance.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>An ogre emerges from a lift in the center of the room
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoran leaps at the ogre, trying to land a killing blow.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoran stabs the ogre in the chest, killing it instantly. He is met by roaring applause from the audience watching from above.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoran stabs the ogre in the chest but fails to kill it instantly. He is bashed by the ogre’s fist dealing damage before it bleeds to death.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>In the following chamber there is an open treasure chest containing gold coins. The chest is also filled with crawling roaches and maggots.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoyu wades through the chest to grab some of the treasure.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoyu is not fazed by the disgusting chest. He finds a considerable amount of gold.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoyu reaches for the chest of coins with bugs. He is grossed out and only manages to grab a small handful of coins.

Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoran was able to successfully open the box finding a valuable gemstone. He adds the gemstone to his pack.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: After too many failed attempts, the box explodes in Haoran’s hand. He suffers damage.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>A ditch of dense noxious gas separates the entrance and exit of this chamber. On the entrance wall is a riddle.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoran attempts to use his wit to solve the riddle.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoran announces his answer and a vent expels the gas. He waits for the gas to dissipate before proceeding.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoran announces his answer and nothing happens. He runs across and suffers damage before pulling a lever dissipating the gas.

Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoran tries to clean enough muck off the wall to see the rune.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoran was able to tolerate the smell and cleans off enough for the rune and the walls begin to glow, revealing to him that there are gemstones along the far wall.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoran tries cleaning off the rune but can’t stomach it for long. He takes a small amount of poison damage.

Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoran consumes the pile of grub.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoran finishes the grubs with no issues. He grabs the handful of jewels that magically appear in the chalice.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Haoran eats the grubs, but to his avail, there were no rewards granted.

Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Haoyu tries to clean off the dagger to their standard and uses it as the offering.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Haoyu places the dagger on the pedestal. He is rewarded with some gold coins.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: The dagger was not clean enough. When Haoyu placed the dagger on the statue’s pedestal, the statue retaliated by shooting a dart at him causing damage.
